description:
What is it: Additional controls for what users can do in Azure, including: registering new applications, accessing the portal, and using LinkedIn connectors. 
 Simeon Notes: Simeon's baseline allows users to register new applications and access the Azure portal, but does not allow LinkedIn connectors. 
 Learn More: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/fundamentals/users-default-permissions#to-restrict-the-default-permissions-for-member-users
